data.description: This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home boasts over 2,000 square feet of living space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by lots of natural light & fresh paint.  This home features 2 living areas, fireplace, a dining area, & the convenience of an attached 2-car garage.  Enjoy the expansive open kitchen, offering ample cabinet space.  With well-spaced neighbors, a generous yard, and located on a corner lot, you’ll enjoy the privacy it offers.    The real magic lies in the IMPORTANT updates that have been meticulously done to make this home exceptional, including a brand-new 200-amp electrical service, a complete overhaul of the plumbing system, featuring new water pipes and drains, & double-pane windows throughout. The durable metal roof ensures minimal maintenance. Stay comfortable year-round with a brand new central HVAC system, & rest easy with the included security system.  Just a short drive away from Cannon Air Force Base, this move-in ready property is ready to show!
